title: Bodenheim station
text: Bodenheim station () is a <a href="railway%20station">railway station</a> in the <a href="Municipalities%20of%20Germany">municipality</a> of <a href="Bodenheim">Bodenheim</a>, located in the <a href="Mainz-Bingen">Mainz-Bingen district</a> in <a href="Rhineland-Palatinate">Rhineland-Palatinate</a>, <a href="Germany">Germany</a>.
